*budget_viewer - TransactionsView

/budget_viewer/transactions/<current_year>
- In this url, the page will load with the default year = the current year
- It will load all transactions for that year.
- Use JQuery to hide all months, except the choosen month
- Use Jquery to hide all incomes or all expenses, based on choosen option
- Provide at the bottom a row with total sum of transactions
- If user chooses another year, take him to:
    /budget_viewer/transactions/<year>
